<p>英 /'bedɪŋ/    美 /'bedɪŋ/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>寝具；铺盖：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bedding was a pillow, a sheet, and a thin quilt. 
寝具包括一个枕头、一张床单和一床薄被。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 2</footer></div></div>